search.query:
index=someindex sourcetype=somesourcetype
| eval HTTP_Category = if(payload.http_status >= 200 AND payload.http_status < 300, "200-299",
if(payload.http_status >= 300 AND payload.http_status < 400, "300-399",
if(payload.http_status >= 400 AND payload.http_status < 500, "400-499",
if(payload.http_status >= 500 AND payload.http_status < 600, "500-599", "Other"))))
| stats count by HTTP_Category
